@cindex  Non-commutative LIBs
@cindex  PLURAL LIBs

@c @sc{Plural} comes with a set of standard libraries. 
@c Their content is described in the following subsections.

The content of libraries, created for non-commutative extensions of
@sc{Singular} like @sc{Plural} and @sc{Letterplace} is described in the following subsections.

Use the @code{LIB} command for loading of single libraries.

@strong{Note:} For any computation in @sc{Plural}, the monomial ordering must be a global ordering.

@menu
* bfun_lib::  Algorithms for b-functions and Bernstein-Sato polynomial
* central_lib:: Computation of centralizer and center in GR-algebras
* dmod_lib:: Fundamental algorithms for algebraic D-modules
* dmodapp_lib::  Applications of algebraic D-modules
* dmodvar_lib:: Algebraic D-modules and Bernstein-Sato polynomial for varieties
* fpadim_lib::  Algorithms for quotient algebras in the letterplace case
* freegb_lib::  Two-sided Groebner bases in free algebras via Letterplace
* involut_lib::  Computations and operations with involutions
* gkdim_lib::  Computation of the Gelfand-Kirillov dimension of modules
* ncalg_lib::  Definitions of important G- and GR-algebras
* ncdecomp_lib::  Algorithmic decomposition of a module with central characters
* ncfactor_lib::  Tools for factorization in some noncommutative algebras
* nctools_lib::  General tools for noncommutative algebras
* perron_lib::  Method of Perron to compute algebraic dependence
* qmatrix_lib::  Quantum matrices, quantum minors and symmetric groups
@end menu

